  "passage": [
    "",
    "Rain fell last night. The river runs fast. Sam and Asha see a tiny duckling near the bridge. |'It looks stuck,' says Asha.",
    "They walk along the bank. The duckling sits on a rock and peeps. A small stick blocks its way. |'We can help,' says Sam.",
    "Sam holds a rope on the bridge post. Asha lies flat and uses a long stick to move the small stick away. The duckling slips into the water and begins to float to its mum. |'We did a rescue!' they cheer.",
    "They watch the duckling reach the nest. The river goes splash in the sun. |'Safe now,' says Asha. They wave and head home."
  ],
